Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 Mike.\N{\fs20}Morning, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.03,0:00:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 星球大戰新的生物出現了\N{\fs20}Hey, the new star wars creatures are out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.72,0:00:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rags最近不太舒服\N{\fs20}Rags hasn't been feeling well lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.77,0:00:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能把他單獨留在家里 所以我就...\N{\fs20}and I can't exactly leave him home alone, so I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了 別說了\N{\fs20}say no more, say no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道這一天會到來的\N{\fs20}I knew this day would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.69,0:00:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}禁止攜帶有自殺傾向的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這牌子上寫的很清楚\N{\fs20}What does that sign say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike  它沒有自殺傾向\N{\fs20}Mike, he's not suicidal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.67,0:00:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Carter 上一次他來辦公室\N{\fs20}Carter, last time he was here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就試圖上碎紙機\N{\fs20}he tried to hump the paper shredder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣吧\N{\fs20}So, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.16,0:00:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 Mike 在這件事上你可大錯特錯了\N{\fs20}Well... You're way off base on this, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的Rags就像23年前一樣快樂\N{\fs20}Rags is as happy today as he was 23 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的\N{\fs20}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很疼吧\N{\fs20}Now that had to hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.28,0:01:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太棒了 Marie阿姨\N{\fs20}This was so great, aunt Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝您的來訪\N{\fs20}Thank you so much for visiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我玩的很開心 Stace 真的\N{\fs20}I had a great time, stace, I really did.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.61,0:01:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 那個你讓我做的必做事項表\N{\fs20}And look, that things-to-do list you made me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.55,0:01:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每項都完成了\N{\fs20}I checked off every one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎 Marie\N{\fs20}You know, Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.64,0:01:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這的整個期間\N{\fs20}The whole time you were here,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都完全對我視而不見\N{\fs20}you completely ignored me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成一項\N{\fs20}Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 我得趕飛機了\N{\fs20}Listen, I gotta catch a plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到大家很高興\N{\fs20}Nice meeting you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎么回事\N{\fs20}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fs20}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.92,0:01:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倆的表情 我了解這種表情\N{\fs20}That look between you. I know that look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是下流的表情\N{\fs20}That's a dirty look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stuart 我都不知道下流表情是什么樣的\N{\fs20}Stuart, I don't even know what a dirty look is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.26,0:01:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做給你看\N{\fs20}Let me show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 太下流了\N{\fs20}Ooh, that's so seedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒做呢\N{\fs20}I haven't even done it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 Owen在嗎\N{\fs20}Hey, is... is Owen here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.77,0:02:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一百萬次告訴你了 不在\N{\fs20}For the millionth time, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一到我就會通知你的\N{\fs20}I will buzz you the second he gets here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪 我從來沒見過你這么興奮\N{\fs20}Jeez, I've never seen you so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來像個小女孩\N{\fs20}You're like a little girl
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等他因為毆打警察被判刑的哥哥出獄\N{\fs20}the morning her brother gets out of jail for beating up a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是圣誕節早晨\N{\fs20}Or Christmas morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是有些緊張\N{\fs20}I'm a little nervous, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.73,0:02:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Owen可是我的導師\N{\fs20}This guy, you know, Owen, was my mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他教會了我關于政治的一切\N{\fs20}He taught me everything I know about politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何競選\N{\fs20}How to campaign...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何操縱媒體\N{\fs20}How to manipulate the press...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的 如何鼓動大眾\N{\fs20}Most importantly, how to motivate people,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當他到達時 我希望大家\N{\fs20}so when he gets here, I want you guys to all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的 呃 做事\N{\fs20}You know... Uh, do... do stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michael Flaherty\N{\fs20}Michael Flaherty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Owen Kingston\N{\fs20}Owen Kingston!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 看看你 我就知道\N{\fs20}Ohhhh, look at you. I tell ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就像 呃 回到過去\N{\fs20}This is, uh... this is like stepping back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs25}演員Christopher Lloyd  在<回到未來>系列中扮演布朗博士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs25}對話出自兩人合作的<回到未來>系列
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去只是序章 Michael\N{\fs20}The past is prologue, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我們這樣的人得面向\N{\fs20}Men like us have to keep looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來\N{\fs20}To the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:02:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底說什么呢\N{\fs20}What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fs20}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次招Michael時他還是個實習生\N{\fs20}When I first hired Michael as an intern
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那時經常早早溜進辦公室\N{\fs20}he used to sneak into the office early
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后假裝自己是參議員\N{\fs20}and play senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想開除他 但他那時已經\N{\fs20}I tried to fire him, but by that time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參與制定通過一些重要的法案\N{\fs20}he had already passed some significant legislation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不覺得有多重要\N{\fs20}I wouldn't call it significant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅燈亮起時允許右轉 是我干的\N{\fs20}Uh, right on red? That was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜圈來了\N{\fs20}Donuts are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 好耶 好耶\N{\fs20}Hey! Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 等下\N{\fs20}Wait, wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 要表達謝意 \N{\fs20}First, let us give thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 Stacy 多謝\N{\fs20}Yeah, ok. Hey, Stacy, thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃鈴鐺圈\N{\fs20}I get the twisty one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是通過禱告\N{\fs20}I meant, uh, with prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michael\N{\fs20}Michael?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 Stacy 你來吧\N{\fs20}Uh, Stacy, wh-why don't you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不\N{\fs20}Hell, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來\N{\fs20}I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 主啊 祝福這饋贈\N{\fs20}Oh, lord, bless this bounty,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們贊美您的榮耀\N{\fs20}and let us revel in your glory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們\N{\fs20}for...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是可憐的罪人\N{\fs20}For we are but wretched sinners...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不值得擁有您神圣的仁愛\N{\fs20}Who are not worthy of your divine benevolence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放松 只是些甜甜圈\N{\fs20}Relax, kid. They're just donuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Paul 謝謝你同意把Rags藏在這里\N{\fs20}Paul, thanks for hiding Rags in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很感謝\N{\fs20}I really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Carter 我們可是朋友\N{\fs20}Carter, please, we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用錢謝就夠了\N{\fs20}Your money is thanks enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些藥是治它的\N{\fs20}Ok, these are his pills for
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘙癢 哮喘 腹瀉\N{\fs20}itching, wheezing, and diarrhea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是抗真菌的\N{\fs20}This is his anti-fungal cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天兩次抹在它肚子上\N{\fs20}Rub that on his tummy twice a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉圈抹\N{\fs20}He likes a circular motion,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別上下抹 它會吐的\N{\fs20}not up and down or he'll vomit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.77,0:04:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要可以減少它的胃脹氣\N{\fs20}This ointment reduces flatulence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用手指蘸一點 輕輕地\N{\fs20}You dip your finger in here... lightly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣 然后溫柔的抹在它的肛門周圍\N{\fs20}like so... and rub it gently on his rectum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這得加錢\N{\fs20}I'm gonna need more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會坐另一輛車\N{\fs20}So I'll take a separate car
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.88,0:04:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后和你在大廈見面 共進晚餐如何\N{\fs20}and meet you at the mansion for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fs20}Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Janelle 自從我們約會以來\N{\fs20}And, Janelle, since we've started dating,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我們的生活開始充滿了秘密的計劃\N{\fs20}I know our lives have become full of secret plans
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼鬼祟祟的見面 神秘的化名\N{\fs20}and furtive meetings, mysterious code names.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我知道 有些囧\N{\fs20}Yeah, I know. It can be a little awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 其實我想說的是這挺酷的\N{\fs20}Well, I was gonna say it's pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺像個間諜\N{\fs20}I feel like a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們今晚再見 Randall\N{\fs20}Well, I'll see you tonight, Randall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以叫我性感特工\N{\fs20}Well, you can call me double-o sexy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生 還記得 Owen Kingston嗎\N{\fs20}Sir, you remember Owen Kingston.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  我知道\N{\fs20}Of course. Well, I understand
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是為了千年發展計劃而來的\N{\fs20}you're heading up our millennium project.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市長先生 這是我的榮幸\N{\fs20}Mr. Mayor, it is a great honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高興又見到Mike吧\N{\fs20}Good to see Mike again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 哈哈\N{\fs20}Yeah, ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我培養的這個人還不錯\N{\fs20}I feel like I did a good job on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 是你培養的嗎\N{\fs20}Really? You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思\N{\fs20}Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike有次曾私下和我說過一句話\N{\fs20}You know, something Mike told me personally
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時可是我一生的驕傲之一 他說\N{\fs20}was one of my proudest moments, and I quote,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"我本會學習如何在政界"\N{\fs20}"I could have learned to crawl "
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"摸爬滾打"\N{\fs20}"through the world of politics "
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"但是你卻教會我"\N{\fs20}"but you were the one"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何像個男人堂堂正正行走于政界"\N{\fs20}who taught me how to walk like a man."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰能想到當年這句話現在會\N{\fs20}Who would have thought that was gonna come back
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反過來讓我難堪\N{\fs20}and bite me on the ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生 議員Donne希望與您見面\N{\fs20}Sir, councilman Donne would like to have a word with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會處理的 先生\N{\fs20}Uh, I'll handle that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說你離開政界有些日子了\N{\fs20}So, I hear you've been out of the game for awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確定你還能像Mike說的那么敏銳嗎\N{\fs20}Are you sure you're still as sharp as Mike says?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和你秘書約會多久了\N{\fs20}How long you been dating your secretary?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.33,0:06:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約一周\N{\fs20}About a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,James 這地方真的很討人喜歡\N{\fs20}James, I think this place is really adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笑什么呢\N{\fs20}What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我床上有個女人\N{\fs20}There's a woman on my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,James 我不希望令你緊張什么的\N{\fs20}Look, James, I don't want to make you nervous or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我約會過不少男人\N{\fs20}but even though I've dated a lot of men,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒和他們睡過 我也不知道為什么\N{\fs20}I've never slept with one. I mean, I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我這一生都在等待那個對的人\N{\fs20}maybe it's because I've waited my whole life for the right guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我是那個對的人?\N{\fs20}So, I'm the right guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.66,0:06:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我就是等厭煩了\N{\fs20}No, I'm just really sick of waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教我一切 James\N{\fs20}Teach me everything, James.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是 我甚至不知道做愛需要多長時間\N{\fs20}I mean, I don't even know how long sex is supposed to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般男人 可以堅持6到7分鐘\N{\fs20}Well, with your average guy, it can last, like, 6 or 7 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:07:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我么 我只需要一半的時間\N{\fs20}Me... I can have you out of here in half that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 電話\N{\fs20}Ah, phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答錄機會接的吧\N{\fs20}Won't the machine answer that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答錄機 你以為我是George Jetson嗎\N{\fs20}Machine? Who am I, George Jetson?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}George Jetson 科幻動畫片<杰森一家>人物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么答錄機 Marie\N{\fs20}Machine. Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住 James 我剛離開\N{\fs20}Remember, James. I've just left town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人知道我在這\N{\fs20}No one knows I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 沒事\N{\fs20}Don't worry. I'll be cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fs20}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,James 我是Stuart\N{\fs20}James, it's Stuart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 讓 Stacy的阿姨接電話\N{\fs20}Hey, let me speak to Stacy's aunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 找你的\N{\fs20}Sure. It's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道\N{\fs20}I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的朋友Owen似乎\N{\fs20}So, your friend Owen seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fs20}I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點不正常\N{\fs20}A little out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Carter 這只是第一印象\N{\fs20}Carter, that's just a first impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你第一次見我時 你覺得我是\N{\fs20}When you first met me, you thought I was, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個控制狂 希望身邊所有人都言聽計從\N{\fs20}A control freak who wanted to surround himself with yes men.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 對不對  - 是的  Mike\N{\fs20}- Am I right?  - Yes, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不認為Owen有點\N{\fs20}Don't you think Owen seemed a little, uh, I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過于篤信宗教\N{\fs20}Overly religious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他信教 這又如何\N{\fs20}He found religion, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還希望有朝一日我能找到信仰呢\N{\fs20}Hope to find religion myself someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 當我老了時\N{\fs20}You know, when I'm older
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快死時\N{\fs20}and looking to cut a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 Mike\N{\fs20}Hey, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一個普通人在接杯水\N{\fs20}That's a normal guy getting a glass of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:07:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嘿 Carter  - Owen\N{\fs20}- Hey, Carter.  - Owen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 黑暗的家伙\N{\fs20}Ooh. A dark one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡魔\N{\fs20}Evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡魔\N{\fs20}Evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fs20}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡這樣 是不是\N{\fs20}You like this, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 你喜歡\N{\fs20}Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶\N{\fs20}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正巧是這方面的專家\N{\fs20}Well, I happen to be an expert at this
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為Claudia每到周二就肚子疼\N{\fs20}because Claudia gets a tummy rub every Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完事了 小可愛\N{\fs20}Yeah, all right. That's about all, kiddo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下去吧\N{\fs20}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就乖乖的待在那 Rags 好嗎\N{\fs20}You just stay right there, Rags, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干的好 Owen  那些委員會成員喜歡你\N{\fs20}Great job, Owen. Those committee members loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 就是個老的處事技巧\N{\fs20}Ah, it was an old management trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最容易團結一伙人的方法是\N{\fs20}The easiest way to bond a group
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找個外人 無情的嘲笑他\N{\fs20}is pick an outsider, relentlessly tease him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給他起傻外號\N{\fs20}and give him a goofy nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你成為我們的樂子 零食包\N{\fs20}Thanks for being a good sport, snack pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了這份千年發展計劃提案\N{\fs20}You know, I've been going over this millennium project proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里面有些很好的內容\N{\fs20}There's some great stuff in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你應該淡化那個 呃\N{\fs20}I do think you should tone down the, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界末日 人類滅亡的內容\N{\fs20}The, uh, armageddon end of days rhetoric.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 Michael\N{\fs20}No need to worry, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有好消息\N{\fs20}I have some good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是彌賽亞\N{\fs20}I'm the messiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs23}意指受上帝指派 來拯救世人的救主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很好笑 很棒\N{\fs20}That's... that's a good joke. That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該以這個做開場白 他們會開心的\N{\fs20}You start with that, you're gonna keep 'em light.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 Michael 我是認真的\N{\fs20}Uh, no, Michael. I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天選之人 萬王之王\N{\fs20}The chosen one. The king of kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的耶穌\N{\fs20}The Alpha and the Omega.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你眼前的\N{\fs20}You're looking at...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是他\N{\fs20}Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好消息\N{\fs20}Well, that is good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Owen 如果這是玩笑\N{\fs20}Look, Owen, if this is some kind of joke,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這么說吧 很好笑的\N{\fs20}let me just say, uh, good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽懂了 呃 哈哈\N{\fs20}I get it. That's, uh... Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很震驚 相信我\N{\fs20}I'm as shocked as you are, believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是很大的責任\N{\fs20}This is a big responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是\N{\fs20}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看這個\N{\fs20}Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未完成事項\N{\fs20}Things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅逐邪惡的撒旦和邪惡勢力\N{\fs20}Banish Satan and the forces of evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重建耶路撒冷\N{\fs20}Build the new Jerusalem...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買牛奶\N{\fs20}Buy milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶\N{\fs20}Milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是忘記買牛奶\N{\fs20}I keep forgetting to pick up milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Owen 你不是認真的吧\N{\fs20}Owen, you can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 Michael\N{\fs20}L-look, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我應該獨自完成這些事\N{\fs20}I know I'm supposed to be able to do this all by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟我是上帝之子\N{\fs20}being the son of God and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我感到許多壓力\N{\fs20}but I'm feeling a lot of pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就想 也許你可以幫助我\N{\fs20}so I was thinking... maybe you could help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我幫你 幫什么\N{\fs20}You want me to help you, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅逐撒旦 建立上帝的王國\N{\fs20}Banish Satan and establish God's kingdom on earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不太忙的話\N{\fs20}If you're not too busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你讓我陷于什么處境嗎\N{\fs20}Do you have any idea the position you've put me in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個很重要的計劃 我擔保了你\N{\fs20}I mean, this is an important project. I vouched for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在市長面前為了你冒風險\N{\fs20}I put myself on the line with the mayor for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Owen 如果媒體決定\N{\fs20}Oh, Owen, if the press decide
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公開的批評這個千年發展計劃項目\N{\fs20}to publicly criticize this millennium program,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我該怎么回應\N{\fs20}how do you think I should respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝應該摧毀那些違抗你意志的人\N{\fs20}Thou shall smite those who defy your will...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩著他們\N{\fs20}From the soles of your feet
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的頭顱前進\N{\fs20}to the crowns of their heads!
