Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來這里來看你\N{\fs20}I came here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你 Michael\N{\fs20}I miss you, Michael.
