Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的第一準則是\N{\fs20}of leading an effective campaign staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要以為自己知道所有的答案\N{\fs20}Don't think you know all the answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要以為自己知道所有的答案\N{\fs20}Don't think you know all the answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.77,0:19:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的Rags\N{\fs20}Poor Rags.
