Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Carter\N{\fs20}Carter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Carter 他活了\N{\fs20}Carter, he's alive!
