Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太高興了\N{\fs20}Oh, I'm so happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個好朋友\N{\fs20}You are such a good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 Carter\N{\fs20}Aw, Carter, aw...
